  <name>Filmmaker</name>
  <summary>Create and edit videos and movies</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A simple video editor for making videos and movies. All actions 
      are non-destructive and automatically saved, so there's no need 
      to worry about losing your work.
    </p>
    <p>
      Additional features include:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Subtitle editing</li>
      <li>Sharing to social media</li>
      <li>Green screen effects</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
